<template id="markdown-editor-template">
	<div class="editor-container">
		<div class="editor-actions">
			<button type="button" title="Gras" class="editor-action-bold" data-markdown-tag data-start="**"><i class="mdi mdi-format-bold"></i></button>
			<button type="button" title="Italique" class="editor-action-italic" data-markdown-tag data-start="*"><i class="mdi mdi-format-italic"></i></button>
			<button type="button" title="Barré" class="editor-action-strikethrough" data-markdown-tag data-start="~~"><i class="mdi mdi-format-strikethrough"></i></button>
			<button type="button" title="Surligné" class="editor-action-highlight" data-markdown-tag data-start="=="><i class="mdi mdi-format-color-highlight"></i></button>
			<button type="button" title="Titre" class="editor-action-header" data-function="addHeader"><i class="mdi mdi-format-header-pound"></i></button>
			<button type="button" title="" class="editor-action-subscript" data-markdown-tag data-start="~"><i class="mdi mdi-format-subscript"></i></button>
			<button type="button" title="Exposant" class="editor-action-superscript" data-markdown-tag data-start="^"><i class="mdi mdi-format-superscript"></i></button>
			<button type="button" title="Liste non ordonnée" class="editor-action-list-bulleted" data-markdown-line="- "><i class="mdi mdi-format-list-bulleted"></i></button>
			<button type="button" title="Liste ordonnée" class="editor-action-list-numbered" data-markdown-line="1. "><i class="mdi mdi-format-list-numbered"></i></button>
			<button type="button" title="Liste à cocher" class="editor-action-list-checkbox" data-markdown-line="- [ ] "><i class="mdi mdi-format-list-checkbox"></i></button>
			<button type="button" title="Citation" class="editor-action-quotation" data-markdown-line="&gt; "><i class="mdi mdi-format-quote-open"></i></button>
			<button type="button" title="Code" class="editor-action-code" data-markdown-tag data-start="`"><i class="mdi mdi-code-tags"></i></button>
			<button type="button" title="Ligne" class="editor-action-line" data-markdown-singleline="---" data-newline><i class="mdi mdi-minus"></i></button>
			<button type="button" title="Note de pied de page" class="editor-action-footnote" data-function="addFootnote"><i class="mdi mdi-format-section"></i></button>
			<button type="button" title="Lien" class="editor-action-link" data-function="addLink"><i class="mdi mdi-link"></i></button>
			<button type="button" title="Image" class="editor-action-image" data-function="addImage"><i class="mdi mdi-image-outline"></i></button>
		</div>
		<textarea class="editor-content" rows="30">
# Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. 

Curabitur **congue** dui est, ac *varius* neque facilisis in. 
Mauris ~~nec~~ eros lacus. Ut ==efficitur== mollis dui vel placerat. 
Etiam ut velit eget erat auctor varius vel auctor libero. 

## Aliquam ipsum enim, accumsan ac interdum ut, dignissim vel elit. 

Morbi nec lacinia magna. 


## Sed sodales urna a mauris blandit rutrum. 

Integer vestibulum laoreet leo, vel rutrum ex ultricies vitae.		
		</textarea>
		<details>
			<summary>Aperçu</summary>
			<div class="editor-preview"></div>
		</details>
		
	</div>
</template>

